name: Blue-Eyes Alternative Ultimate Dragon
desc:
"Blue-Eyes White Dragon" + "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" + "Blue-Eyes White Dragon"
Your opponent cannot target this card with card effects, also it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's card effects.  Once per turn: You can target 1 card your opponent controls; destroy that target. If this card was Fusion Summoned using “Blue-Eyes Alternative White Dragon” as material, you can target up to 3 cards instead. This card cannot attack the turn this effect is activated.
str2: Summoned with "Blue-Eyes Alternative White Dragon" as material
